{
  "texts": [
    "dbo.TrafficIndex 9 Statistical traffic performance data for each defined road segment.In this context, we propose an intelligent traffic performance chatbot TP-GPT for real-time transportation surveillance and management in a privacy-preserving way.",
    "While, technical problems need to be tackled for comprehensive development: 1) ChatGPT does not have preliminary contextual knowledge of the database setup, structures and content.",
    "Even though ChatGPT has strong abilities in programming and inference, direct deployment of the language model to database analysis without prerequisites may result in hallucination that blind actions irrelevant to the raised question would possibly be taken.",
    "Thus, the compilation of appropriate input prompts is essential for employing ChatGPT.",
    "2) ChatGPT has a reliable performance of executing sequential commands activated by human's input."
  ]
}